  <brief_title>Dexamethasone Iontophoretic Patch for the Treatment of Pain Associated With Lateral Epicondylitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of a Dexamethasone Iontophoretic Transdermal Patch for the Treatment of Pain Associated With Lateral Epicondylitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
